  "slug": "meatball-adobo-with-shrimp-fried-rice-and-egg",
  "name": "Meatball Adobo with Shrimp Fried Rice and Egg",
  "recipe_type": "breakfast",
  "brief_description": "Meatball Adobo with Shrimp Fried Rice and Egg is something that I came-up with after combining two dishes that I recently prepared. I had this meal for breakfast and it was the first time that I will be having both together as a meal.",
  "cuisine": "Filipino",
  "instructions": [
    {
      "position": 1,
      "text": "Prepare the adobo meatball and shrimp fried rice according to the recipe provided in the links above."
    },
    {
      "position": 2,
      "text": "In 4 to 6 individual plates, arrange a portion of the fried rice and adobo meatballs. Top with fried egg. your fried egg does not need to be perfect, unless you really insist."
    },
    {
      "position": 3,
      "text": "Serve for either breakfast, lunch or dinner. This can also be a good \"baon\" for school or for the office."
    },
    {
      "position": 4,
      "text": "Share and enjoy!"
    }
  ],
